00039 /* run the filter */
00040 
00041 void filter_OvSv( FiltOvSv pflt )
00042 {
00043     int i,
00044         j,
00045         m = pflt->fftlen,
00046         n = pflt->buflen;
00047     COMPLEX *zfvec = pflt->zfvec,
00048         *zivec = pflt->zivec,
00049         *zovec = pflt->zovec,
00050         *zrvec = pflt->zrvec;
00051     REAL scl = pflt->scale;
00052 
00053     /* input sig -> z */
00054     //fftw_one(pflt->pfwd, (fftw_complex *) zrvec, (fftw_complex *) zivec);
00055     fftwf_execute( pflt->pfwd );
00056 
00057     /* convolve in z */
00058     for ( i = 0; i < m; i++ )
00059         zivec[i] = Cmul( zivec[i], zfvec[i] );
00060 
00061     /* z convolved sig -> time output sig */
00062     //fftw_one(pflt->pinv, (fftw_complex *) zivec, (fftw_complex *) zovec);
00063     fftwf_execute( pflt->pinv );
00064 
00065     /* scale */
00066     for ( i = 0; i < n; i++ )
00067         zovec[i].re *= scl, zovec[i].im *= scl;
00068 
00069     /* prepare input sig vec for next fill */
00070     for ( i = 0, j = n; i < n; i++, j++ )
00071         zrvec[i] = zrvec[j];
00072 }

00074 void reset_OvSv( FiltOvSv pflt )
00075 {
00076     memset( ( char * ) pflt->zrvec, 0, pflt->fftlen * sizeof( COMPLEX ) );
00077 }

00081 /* info: */

00083 /* NB strategy. This is the address we pass to newCXB as
00084    the place to read samples into. It's the right half of
00085    the true buffer. Old samples get slid from here to
00086    left half after each go-around. */
00087 COMPLEX *FiltOvSv_initpoint( FiltOvSv pflt )
00088 {
00089     return &( pflt->zrvec[pflt->buflen] );
00090 }

00124 /* how many samples to take */
00125 
00126 /* NB strategy. This is the number of good samples in the
00127    left half of the true buffer. Samples in right half
00128    are circular artifacts and are ignored. */
00129 int FiltOvSv_storesize( FiltOvSv pflt )
00130 {
00131     return ( pflt->fftlen - pflt->buflen );

00136 /* create a new overlap/save filter from complex coefficients */
00137 
00138 FiltOvSv newFiltOvSv( COMPLEX * coefs, int ncoef, int pbits )
00139 {
00140     int buflen,
00141         fftlen;
00142     FiltOvSv p;
00143     fftwf_plan pfwd,
00144                pinv;
00145     COMPLEX *zrvec,
00146            *zfvec,
00147            *zivec,
00148            *zovec;
00149 
00150     p = ( FiltOvSv ) safealloc( 1, sizeof( filt_ov_sv ),
00151                                 "new overlap/save filter" );
00152     buflen = nblock2( ncoef - 1 ), fftlen = 2 * buflen;
00153     zrvec = newvec_COMPLEX_fftw( fftlen, "raw signal vec in newFiltOvSv" );
00154     zfvec = newvec_COMPLEX_fftw( fftlen, "filter z vec in newFiltOvSv" );
00155     zivec = newvec_COMPLEX_fftw( fftlen, "signal in z vec in newFiltOvSv" );
00156     zovec = newvec_COMPLEX_fftw( fftlen, "signal out z vec in newFiltOvSv" );
00157 
00158     /* prepare frequency response from filter coefs */
00159     {
00160         int i;
00161         COMPLEX *zcvec;
00162         fftwf_plan ptmp;
00163 
00164         zcvec = newvec_COMPLEX( fftlen, "temp filter z vec in newFiltOvSv" );
00165         //ptmp = fftw_create_plan(fftlen, FFTW_FORWARD, pbits);
00166         ptmp =
00167             fftwf_plan_dft_1d( fftlen, ( fftwf_complex * ) zcvec,
00168                                ( fftwf_complex * ) zfvec, FFTW_FORWARD,
00169                                pbits );
00170 
00171 #ifdef LHS
00172         for ( i = 0; i < ncoef; i++ )
00173             zcvec[i] = coefs[i];
00174 #else
00175         for ( i = 0; i < ncoef; i++ )
00176             zcvec[fftlen - ncoef + i] = coefs[i];
00177 #endif /*  */
00178 
00179         //fftw_one(ptmp, (fftw_complex *) zcvec, (fftw_complex *) zfvec);
00180         fftwf_execute( ptmp );
00181         fftwf_destroy_plan( ptmp );
00182         delvec_COMPLEX( zcvec );
00183     }
00184 
00185     /* prepare transforms for signal */
00186     //pfwd = fftw_create_plan(fftlen, FFTW_FORWARD, pbits);
00187     //pinv = fftw_create_plan(fftlen, FFTW_BACKWARD, pbits);
00188     pfwd =
00189         fftwf_plan_dft_1d( fftlen, ( fftwf_complex * ) zrvec,
00190                            ( fftwf_complex * ) zivec, FFTW_FORWARD, pbits );
00191     pinv =
00192         fftwf_plan_dft_1d( fftlen, ( fftwf_complex * ) zivec,
00193                            ( fftwf_complex * ) zovec, FFTW_BACKWARD, pbits );
00194     /* stuff values */
00195     p->buflen = buflen;
00196     p->fftlen = fftlen;
00197     p->zfvec = zfvec;
00198     p->zivec = zivec;
00199     p->zovec = zovec;
00200     p->zrvec = zrvec;
00201     p->pfwd = pfwd;
00202     p->pinv = pinv;
00203     p->scale = 1.0 / ( REAL ) fftlen;
00204 
00205     return p;
00206 }

00208 /* deep-six the filter */
00209 void delFiltOvSv( FiltOvSv p )
00210 {
00211     if ( p )
00212     {
00213         delvec_COMPLEX_fftw( p->zfvec );
00214         delvec_COMPLEX_fftw( p->zivec );
00215         delvec_COMPLEX_fftw( p->zovec );
00216         delvec_COMPLEX_fftw( p->zrvec );
00217         fftwf_destroy_plan( p->pfwd );
00218         fftwf_destroy_plan( p->pinv );
00219         safefree( ( char * ) p );
00220     }
00221 }
